# Plan: Default Quantity & Barcode Search Refinement

## Goal
1. When a user successfully scans a barcode, the default "정상수량" (Normal Quantity) should be automatically set to `1` instead of `0` to speed up the workflow.
2. Verify / Refine the barcode search behavior. The user states "상품코드랑 바코드랑 다른거야 바코드로 검색할수있어야돼" - Currently, the API searches [(ProductMaster.barcode == barcode) | (ProductMaster.code == barcode)](file:///c:/Users/dkstk/.gemini/antigravity/database.py#17-23). We should ensure the frontend clearly treats the scanned input as a barcode and sends it to the API correctly. If there is a bug with the specific column upload, we will refine the upload mapping to ensure `SCAN_CODE` is correctly saved to `barcode` and `ITEM_CODE` is correctly saved to `code`.

